com.hazelcast.jet.function

Interface FunctionEx<T,R>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Function<T,R>, Serializable
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface FunctionEx<T,R>
extends Function<T,R>, Function<T,R>, Serializable
    Serializable variant of java.util.function.Function which declares checked exception.
    Since:
    3.0
